Ingredients/B-Complex Vitamins

B-Complex Vitamins

VitaminsEssential Capsules
Description

Complete B-vitamin complex including Thiamin (B1), Riboflavin (B2), Niacin (B3), B6, Folate (B9), and B12. Essential for energy metabolism, brain function, and cellular processes.

Molecular Formula: Multiple

Mechanism of Action

Coenzymes for energy metabolism (ATP production), neurotransmitter synthesis, DNA/RNA synthesis, and methylation reactions

Blueprint Dosage

Various (see individual B vitamins)
